# openlineage_job

Records an OpenLineage `JobEvent` and its full lineage metadata as a JSON file.
One file is written per job at `{output_dir}/job__{namespace}__{name}.json`
(slashes in namespace/name are replaced with dashes).
The file contains the raw OpenLineage JobEvent alongside metadata for auditing.

This resource enables **all** OpenLineage job and dataset facets — schema,
documentation, source code, SQL, tags, column lineage, and more. Use the
full example below as a reference for the complete facet vocabulary.

